      "message": "Thanks for the quick review!\n\nWould you mind if I add a testcase to `test/asf/test_vcl.py`, to avoid this issue popping up again?\n\nBy the way, we should probably also do something about the VPP process just throwing a oom segfault when the control queue runs full, so it is a bit more resilient. My idea would be to cut the connection and raise a error in VCL.\nI\u0027d be happy to wire up a CL, once I know what the right approach is.\nWhat would be a good place to discuss this, probably the ML?",
      "revId": "9bd0d4547cf3f7d4b7b56de9d6158b782865b9f3",
