      "side": 1,
      "message": "Regarding the test, sure. If it gets too complicated test/hs-test. \nRegarding the segfault, if one wants to protect vpp in these types of situations, probably the best option is use-private-rx-mqs in session stanza in vpp\u0027s startup. That creates per app message queues, so apps don\u0027t overrun vpp\u0027s mqs. \nAnd yes, the best place to discuss these things would be the ML.",
